If we look at the modified test, the SFC doesn't type its props but if it did, it would have to specify that it accepts `intl` (and that it's required) or it would generate a TS error.

Meaning, the following should be equivalent:

```ts
injectIntl<SomeComponentProps & InjectedIntlProps>(({
    intl: {
        formatDate,
        formatHTMLMessage,
         formatNumber,
         formatMessage,
         formatPlural,
         formatRelative,
         formatTime,
         locale,
         defaultLocale
     },
     className
 }: SomeComponentProps & InjectedIntlProps) => ...
);
```

or better abstracted into 

```ts
type Props = SomeComponentProps & InjectedIntlProps;
```

